he Botany Bay was a ship that sailed the waters of Maer Dualdon sometime before the early 14 century DR.
The Botany Bays helm was mounted on the wall of The Salty Dog Tavern in the town of Targos in Icewind Dale. The ships name was inscribed on the wheels wood. It was displayed by the taverns proprietor Gohar as early as the .
